dct_title_s: Bosnia and Herzegovina city graphic 1:15,000 : Banja Luka
dct_description_sm: Relief shown by contours and spot heights. Contour interval 5 meters. Relief shown by 20 meter contour intervals and spot elevations. This sheet falls within NL 33-12, 1501A, 1:250,000 and 2584 I, M709, 1:50,000. "Reprinted by NIMA 8-00." "Cordinate conversiton WGS84 to ED 50." "Grid 1,000 meter UTM zone 33." "Grid 1,000 meter UTM zone 33." Includes index to streets, guide to numbered features, glossary, location map and boundary guides. "NSN 7643014015791." "NIMA Ref. no. M903XBANJALUKA."
dct_creator_sm: United States. National Imagery and Mapping Agency
